title: Lesbian Zombies #3 - NSFW Horror Comedy Comic
description:
Lesbian Zombies from Outer Space, Issue #3 - CBR file

Get issue #3 of the NSFW zom-com seven-part series where flawed male fantasy becomes a nightmare!

Upon the grim realization that Ace's precious Captain Hammer videotapes are missing, and that their vehicle has been destroyed by irrationally destructive lesbian zombies, Ace and Gwen seek shelter for the night in a Catholic church. But is it really wise to shack up in a building full of nuns in the midst of a lesbian zombie apocalypse? Read the book to find out!

24 pages of full-color nudity and violence make this an ADULTS ONLY horror comic.

Find more at www.lesbianzombies.com
